1
00:00:30,860 --> 00:00:33,340
♪Overcoming the boundary of confusion♪

2
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:36,020
♪Holding onto my life
in the face of death threats♪

3
00:00:36,380 --> 00:00:39,300
♪I look into this dark night♪

4
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:44,020
♪Never once has my soul
been extinguished♪

5
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:46,820
♪With this passion♪

6
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:50,940
♪My spirit is growing
to reach full swing♪

7
00:00:51,940 --> 00:00:54,780
♪Slashing the mountain
and the ocean apart♪

8
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:57,180
♪Answering the true call on a sword♪

9
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:01,140
♪I'm the chosen one
in this turbulent world♪

10
00:01:02,340 --> 00:01:05,260
♪Keep my distance from the world♪

11
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,100
♪Who can understand my loneliness♪

12
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:11,180
♪A single thought, looking down♪

13
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:14,340
♪Blades unsheathed,
frost flies everywhere♪

14
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:17,100
♪A belief that cuts through the world♪

15
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,100
♪Soaring towards the sky,
the sword reigns all♪

16
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:24,900
♪Striding across the land
with a drunken gait♪

17
00:01:25,140 --> 00:01:27,700
♪I will protect the people
whenever I'm needed♪

18
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:31,820
♪Atop the summit, you and I shall
battle for the world's best♪

19
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:34,700
[Directed by Chen Zhoufei]

20
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:42,320
[Dashing Youth]

21
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:46,820
[Based on "Zhou Munan's
Juvenile Martial Arts Series"]

22
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:49,020
[from fanqienovel.com and bkneng.com]

23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020
[Episode 6]

24
00:01:55,860 --> 00:01:56,500
Young Lady.

25
00:01:56,980 --> 00:01:58,020
If my calculation is right,

26
00:01:58,140 --> 00:01:59,340
the White-Haired Deity
and Marquis Purple Robe

27
00:01:59,340 --> 00:02:01,220
should arrive at Sky's Beyond by now.

28
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:03,540
If Second Young Lady sees them

29
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:04,980
but not you,

30
00:02:05,060 --> 00:02:06,540
she'll be angry.

31
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:10,020
I asked them to leave first

32
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:12,020
because I wanted

33
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,580
to visit lands
that once belonged to Beique.

34
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,860
I'm sure Qing won't be mad at me

35
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:18,900
once she hears my reason.

36
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:28,740
Young Lady, there's a house there.

37
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:37,060
[Sky's Beyond]

38
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:39,980
Come in.

39
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,420
Sir,

40
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:48,300
the Western Chu's Sword Song
has appeared

41
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,940
and the innate martial artist
has been found.

42
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:54,580
After the Sword Deity fell,

43
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:57,140
his body was hung by the city wall.

44
00:02:57,220 --> 00:02:58,860
I saw it with my own eyes.

45
00:03:01,540 --> 00:03:04,180
Only the Scholar Deity could pass

46
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:06,460
down the Western Chu's Sword Song now.

47
00:03:07,940 --> 00:03:08,780
The Scholarly Deity...

48
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,300
The Art of Drugs...

49
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:15,860
The revival of our country is soon.

50
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:22,420
[Wuxiang, Lord, Sky's Beyond]

51
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:41,660
Young Lady,

52
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,140
the person they worship

53
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,900
is Emperor Gouchen from our Beique.

54
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:48,580
They are our subjects.

55
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:53,500
I saw the dates on your memorial tablet.

56
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:56,100
Did your spouse and father-in-law

57
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,100
pass away 15 years ago?

58
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:00,420
My husband and my father-in-law

59
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:02,100
died in the battle

60
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,220
between Beique and Beili

61
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:06,420
15 years ago.

62
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,740
Have you ever thought

63
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:12,980
Beique would be rebuilt one day?

64
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,900
Even if Beique is rebuilt, so what?

65
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,460
My husband

66
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:20,900
and my son

67
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:24,260
can never return to me.

68
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:29,540
When another war begins,

69
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:31,940
how many more women

70
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:35,540
will lose their husbands

71
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,900
and children?

72
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:40,340
Why should we

73
00:04:41,660 --> 00:04:43,460
rebuild the country then?

74
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:49,140
Young Lady,

75
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,140
what's in your mind?

76
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:54,980
If we travel north for another 20 li,

77
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:57,580
we will arrive at the former capital.

78
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:00,140
Every Lantern Festival,

79
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:01,900
it would be illuminated by lanterns.

80
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:04,020
I thought that was

81
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:08,020
the most beautiful scene in the world.

82
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,500
But it seems like

83
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,780
regardless of whether it's a capital

84
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:16,300
of a certain nation,

85
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:19,100
or if it's still run

86
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,660
by the same person,

87
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:24,060
when there's peace,

88
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:26,740
it will continue

89
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:30,980
to be illuminated by lanterns
during the festival.

90
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,820
Our life is short.

91
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:43,300
Perhaps the adherents of Beique

92
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:49,260
don't need to rebuild Beique,

93
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:51,700
but rather peaceful moments

94
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:54,500
like tonight.

95
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:11,020
Western Chu's Sword Song's
Cosmic Path.

96
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:13,380
Everyone respects and avoids it.

97
00:06:13,380 --> 00:06:15,460
Find its Sly Path
so that it can be of my use.

98
00:06:15,540 --> 00:06:17,540
But if it endangers
the Baili Family, you shall retreat.

99
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:23,060
Father.

100
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:24,620
I'd love

101
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:26,220
to witness the Cosmic Path myself.

102
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:31,220
Father sent a missive?

103
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:33,460
He said

104
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,820
that beneath the Cosmic Path
lied the Sly Path.

105
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,860
Common people can have the Cosmic Path.

106
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,180
The Wen Family can have the Sly Path.

107
00:06:40,700 --> 00:06:42,780
What is the Sly Path?

108
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:44,260
I've heard of it,

109
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:46,660
but not seen it.

110
00:06:47,220 --> 00:06:50,060
It's said it's something
about Western Chu's Art of Drugs.

111
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:51,940
If that exists,

112
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:54,220
even the deities and ghosts fear it.

113
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:55,660
What if we can't find it?

114
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:58,020
I wonder too.

115
00:06:58,580 --> 00:06:59,980
If we can't find it,

116
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,260
will you help the Baili Family

117
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:04,020
or the Wen Family?

118
00:07:08,340 --> 00:07:10,660
I'll ask my son.

119
00:07:11,020 --> 00:07:13,260
I'll help whoever he wants me to help.

120
00:07:15,980 --> 00:07:16,900
Don't worry.

121
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,620
Father said

122
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:19,900
that if it endangered the Baili Family,

123
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:21,460
we retreat.

124
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:24,380
He told you to retreat,

125
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:26,380
not to assist them.

126
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:31,020
It means he has noticed

127
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,500
it's different this time.

128
00:07:36,740 --> 00:07:37,940
But Father can only represent himself.

129
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,100
I'm different from him.

130
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,740
I don't care about the Baili Family,

131
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:43,100
but I will not let anyone harm you,

132
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:44,540
not to mention my nephew.

133
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:46,620
Unless...

134
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:50,140
I die.

135
00:07:55,500 --> 00:08:01,060
[I'll poison you to death]

136
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:24,900
I wonder

137
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:26,580
how Sikong Changfeng is doing now.

138
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:45,180
[Drug King Valley]

139
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:13,980
[Xin Baicao, Drug King]

140
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:50,420
Thank you, sir.

141
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:52,140
No need to thank me.

142
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:54,780
I didn't say I'd save you.

143
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:58,180
Tell me.

144
00:09:58,740 --> 00:09:59,780
Did Wen Hujiu ask you

145
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:00,540
to come here?

146
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,140
Did he say

147
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:04,060
that when I saw the poison in you,

148
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:06,100
I'd do my best to cure you

149
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:08,100
to prove that I was better than him?

150
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:09,660
And once I fed you the antidote,

151
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,300
your previous injuries would flare up.

152
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:13,540
I'd think that it was
another trick from him

153
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:15,420
and so I'd do my very best

154
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:16,860
to save you once more.

155
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,380
Oh, no.

156
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:20,060
Mr. Wen told me

157
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:21,420
that the Drug King would save me,

158
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,260
but he didn't tell me what to do

159
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:24,700
if he saw through the plan.

160
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:27,580
Only one person can put

161
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:29,660
those five poisons in a body.

162
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:31,140
No one else can do that.

163
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:34,180
Therefore, only he
can pull off such a childish trick.

164
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:40,700
Don't move.

165
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:43,260
If you won't save me,

166
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:45,700
then I won't stay here.

167
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:47,780
I didn't say I wouldn't save you.

168
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,300
However,

169
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:50,660
I have a condition.

170
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:53,220
What is it?

171
00:10:53,620 --> 00:10:54,540
By right,

172
00:10:55,460 --> 00:10:57,780
you should have been dead.

173
00:10:58,140 --> 00:10:59,620
What kept you alive?

174
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:02,060
Did a famous physician treat you before?

175
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:05,820
I have no money for a physician.

176
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:08,500
I saw a book about herbs,

177
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:11,180
gathered some herbs,

178
00:11:11,780 --> 00:11:12,900
and ingested them randomly.

179
00:11:13,180 --> 00:11:14,420
How quaint.

180
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:17,500
You might have a talent
for medicinal knowledge.

181
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:19,620
Great.

182
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:20,900
I need

183
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:23,060
an apprentice here to test my herbs

184
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:24,740
and to serve me.

185
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,180
He may follow my steps

186
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,660
after I pass away

187
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:29,460
and become a drug king.

188
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:32,620
You're too old to be an apprentice,

189
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:34,380
but I have no other candidates here.

190
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:36,860
I'll just have to make do.

191
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:38,460
Farewell.

192
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:41,860
Fine. Six months.

193
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:43,420
I'll save you

194
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:45,500
and you keep me company
here for six months.

195
00:11:47,460 --> 00:11:48,460
Just six months?

196
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:49,540
Yes.

197
00:11:50,780 --> 00:11:52,180
Maybe after six months,

198
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:55,300
you'll want to stay.

199
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:03,660
Sure.

200
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:14,180
What's the matter?

201
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:17,580
Sir,

202
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,260
it's Mr. Zhuomo.

203
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:24,740
Heading to Qiandong City, Feng?

204
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:26,620
I knew that

205
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:27,700
with your temperament,

206
00:12:27,780 --> 00:12:28,900
you would

207
00:12:28,940 --> 00:12:30,300
rush here at once.

208
00:12:30,460 --> 00:12:31,180
And,

209
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:32,300
with my wit,

210
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:33,780
I know that you'll pass by here.

211
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:34,540
What do you think?

212
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:35,460
Isn't my prediction

213
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:36,380
precise?

214
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:37,620
Compliment me.

215
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,020
Father.

216
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:58,500
I have news from Tianqi City.

217
00:13:01,420 --> 00:13:03,180
It's about the Little Master
from the Academy.

218
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:26,340
My dear father.

219
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:27,940
The sun hasn't even come out yet.

220
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:29,180
What are you doing?

221
00:13:29,460 --> 00:13:31,940
Your uncle told me
that you wanted to learn swordsmanship.

222
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:34,100
So get up and practice.

223
00:14:12,380 --> 00:14:13,740
You little brat.

224
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,900
He falls asleep here.

225
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,620
How rude.

226
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:22,900
Carry your sword.

227
00:14:23,260 --> 00:14:24,460
A good swordsman

228
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,820
does not put his sword away randomly.

229
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:27,300
Are you going to teach me?

230
00:14:29,300 --> 00:14:30,820
Isn't it obvious?

231
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:33,780
I don't want you to teach me.

232
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:34,820
Why?

233
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:36,940
You don't think I'm good enough?

234
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:40,620
Look.

235
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:42,220
What do you think of this sword?

236
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:44,820
Celestial Level Sword
is naturally among the best ones.

237
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:46,580
Yes.

238
00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:48,660
If I have the best sword,

239
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:49,980
I must be tutored

240
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:51,220
by the greatest swordsman.

241
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,380
Mr. Li from Jixia Academy

242
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,140
in Tianqi City is the strongest

243
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:56,660
individual at the moment.

244
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:58,180
Since I can't head to Tianqi City,

245
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,140
just find me

246
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:00,900
someone of his caliber.

247
00:15:02,700 --> 00:15:04,060
What a brat.

248
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:29,220
Like I said,

249
00:15:29,460 --> 00:15:30,500
a good swordsman

250
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:32,140
does not put his sword away randomly.

251
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:33,900
Give it back.

252
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:45,860
There you go.

253
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:47,220
Now, use it.

254
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:49,300
Sure.

255
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:05,140
That's how you wield a sword?

256
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:07,220
Again.

257
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:08,340
Why bother?

258
00:16:09,460 --> 00:16:11,220
Learn how to draw it first.

259
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:15,700
There you go.

260
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:10,700
This is how you draw a sword.

261
00:17:12,180 --> 00:17:13,540
This is the unsheathing technique

262
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:15,260
of my Instant Kill Sword Arts.

263
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:17,100
I could only master the basics

264
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:19,460
of the sword technique
my master taught me.

265
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:21,740
Yet I remember a line

266
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,260
from him.

267
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:26,340
You must have a reason
to draw your sword,

268
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:28,060
and when you sheathe, it means
you have completed your mission.

269
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,940
The sword wave must be fast
like lightning,

270
00:17:30,020 --> 00:17:31,740
yet silent.

271
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:33,020
Always know

272
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:35,700
why you draw your sword.

273
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:38,300
From now on,

274
00:17:38,420 --> 00:17:39,500
you will be confined

275
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:41,260
to this yard.

276
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:43,500
You may only leave

277
00:17:43,580 --> 00:17:45,380
once your unsheathing technique

278
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:46,980
is strong enough

279
00:17:47,660 --> 00:17:50,100
to slice this scarecrow in half.

280
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,140
It's just unsheathing.

281
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:58,620
But that looks cool.

282
00:18:03,980 --> 00:18:07,500
[Ten Days Later]

283
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:10,300
I don't understand.

284
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:11,980
Must we

285
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,580
wear this outfit?

