He only sent

581
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:34,020
his most trustworthy son

582
00:35:34,100 --> 00:35:36,060
to deal with the Scholarly Deity

583
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:37,260
in secret.

584
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:43,060
Chengfeng, once they
are at the courtyard,

585
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:44,860
dispatch more men

586
00:35:45,180 --> 00:35:47,260
to block all ingress and egress.

587
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:50,980
Irrelevant personnel
are not to enter or leave.

588
00:36:30,380 --> 00:36:31,620
Quickly.

589
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:48,940
Jixia?

590
00:36:50,940 --> 00:36:52,460
You're here on behalf of the Academy?

591
00:36:52,940 --> 00:36:53,860
I'd love

592
00:36:53,860 --> 00:36:55,380
to represent the Academy.

593
00:36:55,900 --> 00:36:57,260
Unfortunately,

594
00:36:57,500 --> 00:37:00,140
I'm here
on behalf of the imperial court.

595
00:37:01,860 --> 00:37:04,780
So what do you want?

596
00:37:05,220 --> 00:37:06,980
You are the remnant of Western Chu.

597
00:37:07,540 --> 00:37:08,540
You must be detained

598
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:12,140
and charged
by the Court of Judicial Review.

599
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:13,860
Many people

600
00:37:14,580 --> 00:37:16,180
can do that,

601
00:37:16,460 --> 00:37:18,500
such as the local prefecture,
the Court of Judicial Review,

602
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:20,540
or even the Shadow Guard Office
under the Crown Prince.

603
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:22,260
Why you, a member of the Academy,

604
00:37:22,460 --> 00:37:24,060
are in charge of this?

605
00:37:24,740 --> 00:37:25,540
You must

606
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:27,980
have a unique identity.

607
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:30,460
Your surname is Xiao?

608
00:37:31,180 --> 00:37:32,300
He asked you to come here

609
00:37:33,100 --> 00:37:34,860
to earn some merits

610
00:37:35,500 --> 00:37:36,380
and to earn

611
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:37,700
the achievement

612
00:37:37,700 --> 00:37:39,300
of detaining a Western Chu's remnant
like me.

613
00:37:39,620 --> 00:37:40,580
Sir,

614
00:37:41,300 --> 00:37:43,620
you are indeed someone
who's as powerful as my master.

615
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,220
Among the princes,

616
00:37:49,780 --> 00:37:51,180
which one are you?

617
00:37:51,940 --> 00:37:52,740
I'm the ninth one.

618
00:37:53,180 --> 00:37:54,660
As a swordsman,

619
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:56,100
I have nothing but respect for you.

620
00:37:56,460 --> 00:37:57,100
However,

621
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:59,660
this has nothing to do

622
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,860
with my desire to take you with me.

623
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:03,380
You think

624
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:05,860
you can take me with you?

625
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,060
I would like to try.

626
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:08,740
Oh right.

627
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,300
My name

628
00:38:11,380 --> 00:38:12,860
is Xiao Ruofeng.

629
00:38:17,420 --> 00:38:18,260
I see.

630
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:21,340
Xiao Ruofeng.

631
00:39:06,660 --> 00:39:08,060
Is that all you've got?

632
00:39:08,380 --> 00:39:10,620
Is this the sword technique

633
00:39:11,340 --> 00:39:12,900
taught to you by your master?

634
00:39:13,380 --> 00:39:14,660
My master possesses a sword technique.

635
00:39:15,540 --> 00:39:17,060
He calls it
the second-best sword technique.

636
00:39:17,700 --> 00:39:20,020
I cannot master it,

637
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:22,620
nor am I strong enough to grasp it.

638
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:23,820
However,

639
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:27,060
I also have my own sword technique.

640
00:39:28,820 --> 00:39:29,660
I call it

641
00:39:30,380 --> 00:39:32,060
the third-best sword technique.

642
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:45,660
Great.

643
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:47,540
What a good name.

644
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:51,180
Now, take my sword.

645
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:26,060
Uncle,

646
00:40:26,980 --> 00:40:27,940
what are you doing here?

647
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,180
Did you have a good sleep?

648
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:34,220
How are you, Dongjun?

649
00:40:35,460 --> 00:40:36,460
Mengsha.

650
00:40:36,820 --> 00:40:37,940
You're here too?

651
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:39,940
Wait.

652
00:40:42,340 --> 00:40:43,180
Before I fell asleep,

653
00:40:43,180 --> 00:40:44,420
did I meet someone?

654
00:40:44,860 --> 00:40:46,660
He told me his surname was Xiao.

655
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:48,660
Was I dreaming?

656
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:50,780
He is the Ninth Prince, Xiao Ruofeng.

657
00:40:51,220 --> 00:40:52,900
Also the Little Master from the Academy.

658
00:40:55,220 --> 00:40:56,780
He came for my master.

659
00:40:57,620 --> 00:40:58,780
How smart of you.

660
00:40:58,940 --> 00:41:01,900
But he was also here for you.

661
00:41:03,180 --> 00:41:04,260
I need to see my master now.

662
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:08,220
You finally admitted

663
00:41:08,220 --> 00:41:09,500
that you have a master.

664
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:10,660
I need to save him.

665
00:41:10,660 --> 00:41:11,860
Even if it means I'll die,

666
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:12,580
I'll save him too.

667
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:14,820
Uncle,

668
00:41:14,860 --> 00:41:15,900
I'll give you ten pots
of Plum First blossom.

669
00:41:15,900 --> 00:41:16,620
Let me go.

670
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:18,660
And 20 pots of Frosty Pine,

671
00:41:18,660 --> 00:41:19,660
30 pots of Illusory Moon,

672
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:21,180
plus this Dustless.

673
00:41:21,260 --> 00:41:22,060
You can have them all.

674
00:41:25,980 --> 00:41:27,100
I don't need your sword.

675
00:41:28,020 --> 00:41:29,620
But as for all those liquors
you mentioned,

676
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:30,820
you have to give me all of them.

677
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:32,380
Let's go.

678
00:41:34,420 --> 00:41:35,220
Mr. Zhuomo.

679
00:41:38,060 --> 00:41:39,380
Are you stopping us?

680
00:41:41,380 --> 00:41:42,460
If I'm not mistaken,

681
00:41:42,620 --> 00:41:44,620
he's in the Sovereign Sky Phase.

682
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:46,220
I won't be able to take him out.

683
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:51,980
I'll just tag along.

684
00:42:39,060 --> 00:42:41,740
