692
00:43:33,340 --> 00:43:34,740
Forgive my arrogance.

693
00:43:35,220 --> 00:43:37,940
The young men should be arrogant

694
00:43:38,660 --> 00:43:39,780
and fearless.

695
00:43:42,460 --> 00:43:43,860
You have potential.

696
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:45,460
I won't kill you.

697
00:43:47,700 --> 00:43:48,980
I am not long for this world.

698
00:43:49,740 --> 00:43:50,940
Thus, I am no threat

699
00:43:51,460 --> 00:43:52,780
